Just in case you&#39;re not aware, `const` means &#39;constant&#39;, and is used for immutable variables; it doesn&#39;t mean `constructor`, as it sounds like you&#39;re implying.

And the part that&#39;s throwing the error is 

    const newPost = new Post({
            title: req.body.title,
            description: req.body.description,
            status: req.body.status   
        });

